    "locales": {
      "en": {
        "name": " Smith & Wesson Mk22 Mod0 9x19 'Hush Puppy'",
        "shortName": "MK22 Mod0",
        "description": "The Mk22 Mod0 is a 9x19 pistol based on the Smith & Wesson Model 39, featuring modifications intended for special forces use. The slide can be locked closed to keep the pistol from cycling; this is intended to make it more quiet when used with a suppressor. In addition to the slide lock, the sights were raised to prevent the suppressor from blocking the sight picture and the barrel was threaded to accommodate a suppressor."
      }
